item.title: CVE-2012-2130|2024-08-06T19:26:08.407Z -- polarssl -- polarssl
item.description: A Security Bypass vulnerability exists in PolarSSL 0.99pre4 through 1.1.1 due to a weak encryption error when generating Diffie-Hellman values and RSA keys.
